{"tid":1144853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國報告稱修例嚴重威脅《香港政策法》　中國外交部：不值一駁","createTime":"2019-05-08T10:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T22:14:17.000Z","uid":5195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"605604312ff8eb60159b3daac164433686fb2631","tid":1144853,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:12:11.000Z","msg":"美國國會轄下的美中經濟與安全審查委員會周二（7日）發表研究報告，警告一旦香港特區政府通過修訂《逃犯條例》，將為美國國家安全和在港經濟利益帶來極大風險，嚴重威脅《香港政策法》多項重要條款。在北京，外交部發言人耿爽回應時表示，香港事務完全是中國內政，反對外國勢力干涉香港事務，有關組織對中國一向充滿偏見，他們的所謂報告和說法不值一駁。"},{"pid":"a53052ee4343ddd84c8e788532024b8075dcffa4","tid":1144853,"uid":128417,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"因為駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62726b2a65032e124e47649d63e853c24add8ba1","tid":1144853,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:17:23.000Z","msg":"九唔答八"},{"pid":"8c2aec3ed2a0387fbe6a85f48db6028a317d77d5","tid":1144853,"uid":105219,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:19:00.000Z","msg":"香港事務完全是中國內政<br />\n<br />\n美國嘅香港關係法亦都完全係美國嘅內政"},{"pid":"e6d97295d3c0b231fd0feffd154ebda6d39df8f2","tid":1144853,"uid":251086,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"因為關乎到美國國民，咪關佢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be5e8b62211e26e9da5087b5086903e28fcd347","tid":1144853,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a53052ee4343ddd84c8e788532024b8075dcffa4","tid":1144853,"uid":128417,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:14:29.000Z","msg":"因為駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T10:40:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdded1feb7cc8e2af6e1279dc37fd0ff02408272","tid":1144853,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc